* Dinobot growled as he rolled his optics and thought...*

<Anything! Just get me out of this Hell Hole!>

* He was about to follow Tavatron to where ever she was leading him when he 
suddenly had the urge to stay there, by the Arks doors. He looked back at 
them and tilted his head to one side, he was feeling something...but what?
Dinobot reached up and ran his hand over the smooth surface of the door, 
something was happening...something big!
He looked back at Tavatron, could she feel it as well? Could she feel 
that...something called.
Dinobot looked back at the doors, it called...but what was it? Something he 
knew and knew well...what?
He snarled, it was at the tip of his mind but it wouldn't revile itself. 
Slag!! WHAT WAS IT!!!
Suddenly it came to him, like a blast to the spark!
Dinobot turned around and growled at Tavatron...*

" Prepare yourself, we may soon have company!"
